description: This data comes from the Trust for Public Land. It includes data for New Orleans and several benchmark cities, including: Atlanta, Baton Rouge, Louisville, Memphis, Miami, Nashville, Oklahoma City, Raleigh, and Tampa. This data is for the year 2014.
